| Grants for hadiya@localhost                                  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| GRANT USAGE ON *.* TO `anu`@`localhost`                      |
| GRANT SELECT ON `INVOICE`.`customer` TO `anu`@`localhost`    |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)

